Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.51,0:37:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好\NOkay, Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.15,0:39:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,（法语）大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.26,0:39:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,（缅甸语）你们好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.67,0:39:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,（希伯来语）你好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.78,0:39:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）你好 向大家致敬
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.29,0:39:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,（印尼语）女士们先生们 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.85,0:39:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,（印尼语）再见期待下次再见
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.78,0:39:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,（克丘亚语）用克丘亚语向你们
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.89,0:39:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,（克丘亚语）每一个人问好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.67,0:39:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,（旁遮普语）欢迎你们
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.61,0:39:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,（赫梯语）你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.65,0:39:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,（孟加拉语）你好 愿到处都有和平
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.49,0:39:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）无论你们是谁 你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.08,0:39:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）我们对你们心怀善意
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.06,0:39:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）并带着和平穿梭星际
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.80,0:39:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[左声道 右声道]
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.73,0:39:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,（亚兰语）你好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.30,0:39:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,（荷兰语）向每个人致以诚挚的问候
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.57,0:39:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,（德语）向所有人致以诚挚的问候
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.65,0:39:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,（乌尔都语）愿和平与你们同在
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.79,0:39:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,（乌尔都语）我们代表地球的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.76,0:39:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[（基洛纳区-监视点J3 1990年6月29日）]
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.70,0:39:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,（乌尔都语）欢迎你们
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.58,0:40:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉来晚了\NSorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.25,0:40:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,路上堵死了 我又没法早点走\NTraffic was hell, and I couldn't leave early.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.05,0:40:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 趁还有时间聊聊吧\NLet's just use the time we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.22,0:40:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,今天感觉怎么样 克拉克？\NHow are you today, Clark?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.42,0:40:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你看得我怎么样？\NHow do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.69,0:40:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的 可能有点累吧\NFine. A little tired, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.36,0:40:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我简直糟糕透了\NI look like shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.43,0:40:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我想确认一下\NCan I ask, and there is
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.80,0:40:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,放心回答 没什么对错\Nno wrong answer here, you know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.77,0:40:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在是不是受到酒精影响？\NAre you intoxicated right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.47,0:40:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛这么问？\NWhy you say it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.94,0:40:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么问了？\NLike what?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.84,0:40:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我从周五起就没碰过一滴酒\NI haven't had a drink since Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.71,0:40:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没准儿我这副鬼样子就是因为没喝酒\NIt's probably why I look like shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.05,0:40:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我能问你个事吗？ - 请说\N- Can I ask you something? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.28,0:40:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你把人强制关精神病院过吗？\NYou ever 5150'd someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.28,0:40:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[【加州法律5150条：强制将危险精神病人送院观察】]
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.45,0:40:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这么多年确实有过几次 只要情况需要\NA few times over the years, when it was necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.66,0:40:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那...那...那什么样的情况才算需要？\NWh-wha-what makes it necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.16,0:41:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我认为对方有伤人自残的风险\NIf I believe that the person is a danger to themselves or others,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.49,0:41:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,或者无法自理\Nor they're gravely disabled.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.37,0:41:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,行 行 \NOkay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.54,0:41:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...\NUm...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.94,0:41:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我在店里发现了点情况\NI found something in the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.44,0:41:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好 什么情况\NOkay. What did you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.05,0:41:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.72,0:41:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是个地方 我...\NA place. I f...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.42,0:41:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现了个地方\NI found a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.09,0:41:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,地方？\NA place?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.39,0:41:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 感觉...\NYeah. It's like, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.93,0:41:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉店就那样...\NIt's like the store just, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.66,0:41:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,往外扩了\Ncontinues, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.00,0:41:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吧...店有墙\NIt's like... you know, like there's a wall
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.90,0:41:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,墙后头居然还是店\Nand on the other side of the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.23,0:41:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没完没了地往外扩\Nthe store just keeps going, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.04,0:41:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就像 就像 像个克隆的 \Nlike-like a... like a copy of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.34,0:41:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我猜入口是用镜子什么的给挡住的\NI-I-I figure they're using mirrors or something
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.11,0:41:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定\Nto hide the entrance, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.01,0:41:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我没听明白\NSorry, I'm not following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.84,0:41:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说找到了个之前没发现的房间？\NIs this a room you didn't know about before?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.98,0:41:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.68,0:41:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就是...就是你一进去后\NOkay, so y-y-you go in and, uh, at first
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.71,0:41:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,看着像个...像个写字楼\Nit just looks like a- like an office building.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.75,0:41:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一个巨大的办公室 你懂吧？\NLike a... like a huge office building, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.72,0:42:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,然后...你 你继续往里走\NAnd then, uh... But then you-you keep going,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.76,0:42:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,接着...接着你就发现\Nand then-then you realize
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.89,0:42:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所...所有东西都不对劲\Nth-th-that none of it makes any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.36,0:42:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢...嗯...想象一下\NIt's-it's like, um... Imagine describing a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.93,0:42:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你给个没见过狗的人描述狗\Nto someone who's never seen one before
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.13,0:42:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,然后让那人把狗画出来\Nand then asking them to draw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.80,0:42:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会画对几个地方\NThey might get some things right, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.80,0:42:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但绝不可能全画对\Nbut there's no way they'd get everything right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.57,0:42:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 诡异的在于细节\NYou know, the devil's in the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.84,0:42:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所以远看像只狗\NSo from a distance, you look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.51,0:42:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但凑近一看...\Nyou think you're seeing a dog, but then you look clos--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.94,0:42:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛那样看我？\NWhy are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.78,0:42:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在试着理解\NI'm just trying to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.21,0:42:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,呵\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.05,0:42:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你不像个心理医生 怎么表情都写在脸上\NYou know, for a shrink, you got a terrible poker face.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.59,0:42:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的这些听起来很离奇\NWhat you're saying might sound fantastical,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.72,0:42:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但并不危险\Nbut not dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.59,0:42:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那些办公室里有人吗？\NAre there any people in these offices?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.63,0:42:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没见过 但我能听到\NNot that I've seen. You know, I hear, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.90,0:42:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,听到脚步声 而且...而且我一转眼\NThere's footsteps, an-an-and stuff gets moved around
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.74,0:42:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,东西就被挪了位置\Nwhen I'm not looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.84,0:42:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这听起来很离谱 但你得明白\NI know how this sounds, but you've got to understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.31,0:42:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那地方太大了\Nit's massive in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.94,0:42:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,简直像纽约地铁那么大 懂吧\NLike New-York's-subway-system massive, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.14,0:42:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没准儿里面有好几百人\NFor all I know, there's hundreds of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.68,0:42:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是没看到\NI just haven't seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.15,0:43:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,看\NLook.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.52,0:43:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 这就像个...\NYou see? It's like a...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.12,0:43:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就像个迷宫\NIt's like a maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.26,0:43:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,根本没尽头\NIt just goes on and on and on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.59,0:43:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我有时候真怕自己会迷路\NSometimes I'm scared I'll get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.53,0:43:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那为什么除了你 没人发现这地方？\NWhy do you think no one else has found this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.50,0:43:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我哪知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.87,0:43:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但入口在负一层\NThe entrance is on the subfloor,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.97,0:43:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所以整个结构\Nso the whole structure is
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.97,0:43:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,估计都在地下 懂吧\Nprobably underground, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.01,0:43:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,地图上根本没这个地方\NIt's not on any city maps.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.87,0:43:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,入口根本看不出来 谁会想到去找？\NThe entrances are hidden, so who'd think to look?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.71,0:43:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我没说不信你...\NI'm not saying I don't believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.81,0:43:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 你跟我说\Nbut you told me yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.68,0:43:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你周五就开始戒酒了\Nyou haven't had a drink since Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.55,0:43:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这会不会导致幻.... - 行了\N- Do you think there is a-- - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.29,0:43:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克拉克 - 停 停\N- Clark-- - No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.96,0:43:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果这是真的... - 行 我懂了 多谢您啊\N- If this is true-- - Yeah, I get it. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.46,0:43:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我迟早会带着证据回来\NYou know, I'm gonna come back here with proof
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.03,0:43:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候你得给我好好道歉\Nand you're gonna owe me a serious fucking apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.58,0:44:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,小凯\NKat!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.92,0:44:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,谁呀 来了 来了\NJesus, goddamn, I'm coming! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.53,0:44:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 - 克船长？\N- Hey. - Cap'n Clark?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.43,0:44:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 额... - 等等 等等 小凯 快来\N- Um... - Wait, wait, wait, wait. Kat?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.53,0:44:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我来了 - 快点\N- I'm coming. - Kat!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.90,0:44:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 我来了\NOkay, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.33,0:44:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是这样的... - 搞什么鬼\N- Look-- -What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.00,0:45:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 那个...\NYeah, I'm sorry, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.60,0:45:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你们明天有空吗？\NWhat are you guys doing tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.24,0:45:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢？\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.00,0:45:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我给钱 算加班 顶多两个小时 很快的\NI'll pay you. Two hours. Overtime. Tops.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.94,0:45:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,行 给钱干什么？\NOkay, pay us for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.78,0:45:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,做调研\NResearch.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.75,0:45:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,摄像机还在你们那儿吧？\NYou got the camera, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.08,0:45:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你们能...能再帮我拍点东西吗？\NYou can-you can borrow it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.69,0:45:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,行不行？\NRight?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.96,0:45:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 开始拍了\NOkay, we are rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.66,0:45:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿摆了些东西\NWe got, um, some shit over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.92,0:45:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[车停]
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.73,0:45:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,还有停车牌\NWe got some stop signs
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.60,0:45:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 呃 绳子\Nand, uh... a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.04,0:45:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,拿绳子干嘛？\NWhat's the rope for?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.30,0:45:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,装备\NSupplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.84,0:45:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,呵呵 看来咱们要被他绑了\NOh, great, he's gonna tie us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.98,0:45:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我绑 是要给自己绑好\NNo, we're gonna tie ourselves up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.04,0:45:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,唔 挺重口味的\NHmm. Kinky.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.45,0:45:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼\NWhat the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.85,0:45:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 你还没说清楚\NUh, you still haven't told us
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.01,0:45:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来这儿干嘛？\Nwhat we're doing here, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.05,0:45:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了 做调研\NI did tell you. Research.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.32,0:45:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是调研装备\NThese are supplies, and we're using them for research.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.19,0:45:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没那么难理解吧\NIt's not that hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.62,0:45:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,行 研究什么？\NOkay, research for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.73,0:45:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你得具体点 老哥\NY-you gotta be more specific, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.06,0:46:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我要进门了\NI'm gonna go through the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.40,0:46:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,什么门？\NWhat door?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.93,0:46:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是门\NThat's the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.10,0:46:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我在另一边也贴了框\NI taped an outline on the other side, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.94,0:46:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,以防咱们找不到\Njust to help us find our way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.37,0:46:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿博？ - 怎么了？\N- Bobby? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.74,0:46:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我知道这很离谱 但得听我的\NLook, I know it sounds crazy, but follow my lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.05,0:46:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,懂吗？\NOkay?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.75,0:46:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我想在天亮前赶回来\NI want to be back before sunup.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.68,0:46:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,老哥 现在才晚上九点 你说什么...\NDude, it's like 9 p.m. What the fuck are you talk--
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.12,0:46:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么情况 克拉克 - 卧槽\N- What the fuck! Clark?! - What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.39,0:46:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么做到的？ - 老哥 你...\N- How did you do that? - Dude, did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.16,0:46:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你也看到了吧？他怎么会...呃...\NDid you fucking see that?! H-how did he, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.63,0:46:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在这儿 快进来看看\NI'm right here. Come see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.29,0:46:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼 你居然真的...\NWhat the fuck? D-did you just fucking...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.06,0:46:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？怎么会...\NWhat? How the f...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.13,0:46:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛呢？阿博 快住手\NBobby, stop. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.77,0:46:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我去 - 克拉克 你在哪儿？\N- What the fuck?! - Clark, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.27,0:46:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 你...你看到了没？\NHa! Hey, did you... did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.14,0:46:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他钻哪去了？ - 看到了 阿博 我看到了\N- Where the fuck did he go? - Yes, Bobby, I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.37,0:46:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我去 搞什...\NOh! Where the f--
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.17,0:46:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,踏进来就行 没事的\NJust step through the door, you'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.14,0:46:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,疯了吧 你得先解释清楚\NWhat?! No! Tell us what is going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.15,0:46:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,管他呢 直接...\NYou know what, just...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.65,0:46:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不 阿博 别进去 阿博 快停下 你要干什么？\NNo, Bobby, wait! Bobby! Wait, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.35,0:46:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博\NBobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.08,0:46:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我去啊\NWhat the fuck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.55,0:47:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,老哥\NDude!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.95,0:47:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,老哥 这怎么可能？\NDude, how is this possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.76,0:47:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿博 克拉克 - 行...\N- Bobby! Clark! - Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.03,0:47:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在哪？里面到底是什么地方？\NWhere are you? What the fuck is back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.63,0:47:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没事没事 小凯 没事的\NNo, no, no, Kat, it's good, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.00,0:47:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧进来看看\NJ-just, you gotta come see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.23,0:47:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说...对 你看...\NI mean... Right, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.24,0:47:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你看这 呃...\NYou see, it's, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.91,0:47:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没问题 - 克拉克 这是什么地方？\N- It's fine. - Clark, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.17,0:47:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们在哪？ - 哦\N- Where are we? - Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.97,0:47:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我也正想弄明白呢\NThat's what I'm trying to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.08,0:47:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这...这是谁的东西？\NWhose, um... Whose shit is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.15,0:47:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是你...是你店里的吗？\NIs it-is it... is it part of your store?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.01,0:47:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真有主的话\NIf it belongs to someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.55,0:47:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我还没碰到那个人 - 好吧\N- I haven't met them yet. - Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.32,0:47:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,自从发现这地方 我每晚都来\NI've been in here every night since I found the place,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.19,0:47:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但也就看了个冰山一角\Nand I still barely scratched the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.09,0:47:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,走 我带你们看看\NCome on. I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.46,0:47:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,越往后越有意思\NIt only gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.16,0:47:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真扯... - 嘿 嘿\N- What the fuck... - Hey. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.46,0:47:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得他给我们下药了吧？\NYou don't think he, like, dosed us or something, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.23,0:47:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？没那回事 咱们没磕药\NWhat? No, no, no. We're not on drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.30,0:47:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我嗨了 肯定能感觉到\NI think I'd be able to tell if I was high.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.40,0:47:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在就嗨着呢\NYou are high!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.50,0:47:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,抽草不算\NPot doesn't count.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.84,0:47:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所以...这就像...\NSo, um, it's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.88,0:47:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,像个空办公区？\Nwhat, like an empty office building?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.68,0:48:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在这儿？算是吧 但这地方简直像是\NIn here? Sure. But it's like it was made
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.11,0:48:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一帮嗑嗨了的建筑工盖出来的\Nby a bunch of construction workers on acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.05,0:48:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,居然还搞了个泳池\NThere's even a pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.65,0:48:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有泳池？\NThere's a pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.12,0:48:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 算是吧\NYeah. I mean, kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.02,0:48:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,快跟上\NKeep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.36,0:48:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,“车停”什么鬼？\N"Pots." What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.53,0:48:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不 那是我上次走的路\NYeah, no, no, that's the way I went last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.47,0:48:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,当时我想找个楼梯下去什么的\NYeah, when I was looking for a staircase down or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.57,0:48:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,结果只发现了个...\NOnly thing I found so far is basically more of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.44,0:48:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好的...\NOkay...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.28,0:48:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 其实就是个斜坡\NI don't know, it's like a ramp, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.68,0:48:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这儿 呃...前面\NIt's, uh... It's up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.92,0:48:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就到了\NWe'll be at it in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.05,0:48:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.99,0:48:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这下面总共有多少层？\NHow many floors does it go down?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.29,0:48:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这不能用楼层来...\NIs this not technically...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.86,0:48:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 开始拍了吗？\NOkay. All right, you filming?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.60,0:48:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拍了  - 行\N- Yeah. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.26,0:48:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么非得让阿博下去？\NI don't see why Bobby has to be the one to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.13,0:48:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想去 - 摄像机在他手上\N- I want to. - He's the one with the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.70,0:48:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,相机又没长在他身上\NWell, it's not like it's attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.07,0:48:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,它挂在我学生证上的\NYeah, well, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.64,0:48:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就算长在身上了\Nto my student ID, yeah, it kinda is.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.57,0:48:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要是觉得不对劲 就拽一下 我把你拉上来 明白吧？\NAny trouble, just give a tug, and I'll pull you up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.41,0:49:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不对劲？克拉克 下面有什么不对劲？\NTrouble? Clark, what fucking trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.94,0:49:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有事的\NThere's not going to be any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.21,0:49:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝 宝贝 没事\NBabe, babe, babe, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.55,0:49:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别下... - 真的没事 我没问题\N- No, hey-- - It's good. I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.01,0:49:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 你不用下去\NBaby, you don't have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.71,0:49:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 我就是想看看下面有什么\NNo, it's cool. I-I just want to see what's down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.42,0:49:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不好奇吗？ - 简直是疯了\N- Are you not curious? - This is stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.72,0:49:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能走多远就走多远 - 没事 你看 你看\N- Just go as far as you can. - No, look, look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.45,0:49:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,其实不用绳子也能走下去\NYou can basically walk down without a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.12,0:49:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么 一点也不陡\NIt's fine, and it's not even steep.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.36,0:49:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,行吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.12,0:49:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好 但有一件事\NOkay, just don't... just one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.83,0:49:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,万一我回不来 记得告诉我妈我爱她哦\NIf I don't come back, you'll tell my mom I love her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.13,0:49:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 行 - 那么 走吧\N- Okay. - All right, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.70,0:49:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好 慢慢来\NAll right, just take it slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.30,0:49:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,行\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.97,0:49:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 实际上还挺陡的\NOh, it is actually kind of steep.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.37,0:49:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没事吧？ - 没事\N- You good? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.11,0:49:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拉紧点 别把我摔了 - 放心\N- Just, uh... try not to drop me. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.05,0:49:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,需要放绳子告诉我\NTell me how much you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.35,0:49:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,喔...慢点\NWhoa... Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.29,0:49:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么...喔 喔 喔 操 啊\NWhat the... Whoa! Whoa! Whoa! Fuck! Aah...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.66,0:49:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你上面怎么拉的绳子？\NWhat the fuck are you guys doing up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.26,0:49:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起\NSorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.07,0:49:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,绳子卡在床腿上了\NIt was stuck around the leg of the bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.67,0:50:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧？ - 行 没事\N- Are you okay? - Yeah. Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.97,0:50:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真是绝了\NJesus fucking Christ...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.30,0:50:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,继续放绳子\NJust keep letting me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.14,0:50:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 来了\NAll right. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.96,0:50:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我下来了\NOkay, I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.80,0:50:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,看到什么没？\NSee anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.13,0:50:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...\NUgh...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.20,0:50:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 就是...\NUh, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.67,0:50:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一堆脏衣服和垃圾\NIt's a bunch of laundry and shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.51,0:50:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思？衣服？\NWhat do you mean? Clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.58,0:50:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,对 这下面真是臭死了\NYeah, it just fucking stinks down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.11,0:50:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么吗？\NSee anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.48,0:50:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有 呃...给我点时间\NYeah, just, uh... Just give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.21,0:50:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.85,0:50:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\NOh, god...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.66,0:51:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[结束南非种族隔离]
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.60,0:51:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼？\NWhat the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.00,0:51:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[【结束南非种族隔离：是80年代盛行的现实世界口号】]
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.04,0:51:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博？\NBobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.54,0:51:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.37,0:51:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就想确认下你没事\NJust checking that you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.14,0:51:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我没事 只是 呃...\NYeah, I'm fine. Just, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.95,0:51:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.08,0:51:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.02,0:51:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.33,0:51:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼？\NWhat the fuck...?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.94,0:51:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博？快上来\NBobby? Come back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.34,0:51:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我心里发毛\NI don't like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.21,0:51:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 呃...再多放点绳子\NHey! Uh... Let some more line out!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.64,0:51:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 已经到头了\NI can't! It's as far as it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.68,0:51:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\NFuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.02,0:52:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我操 快拉我上去\NFuck! Pull me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.22,0:52:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博 怎么了？\NBobby! What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.76,0:52:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 操 - 你看到了什么？\N- Fuck! - What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.59,0:52:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,磨蹭什么 快把他拉上来\NWhat the fuck is it? Pull him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.93,0:52:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我在拉啊 我的天 - 操\N- I am! Jesus Christ! -Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.13,0:52:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,拉快点\NPull harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.43,0:52:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,快拉 老哥 搞什么鬼\NPull, man! What the fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.77,0:52:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,绳子绕到我脚上了\NIt's getting caught on my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.43,0:52:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 绳子绕到我脚上了 - 快点使劲拉\N- I can't pull-- - Fucking pull harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.24,0:52:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 快点拉\NClark, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.74,0:52:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,快到了 快到了 宝贝 坚持住\NAlmost here! Almost here, babe, just a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.68,0:52:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快把他拉上来 - 你看到了什么？\N- Pull him up! - What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.84,0:52:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,下...下面有人\NThere's, uh, there's someone down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.75,0:52:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你安全了...什么？- 操\N- We've got you. What? - Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.28,0:52:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,慢点说 深呼吸 宝贝 没事了\NSlow down, just breathe. Baby, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.92,0:52:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,快把这破玩意儿给我解开 操 真是够了\NJust get this shit off me, man. Fuck. Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.68,0:52:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没事了 没事了 - 你看到了什么？\N-I t's okay. It's okay. - What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.99,0:52:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来 深呼吸 - 这打的什么破结？\N- Here. Hey, deep breath. - What kind of knot is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.15,0:52:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,深呼吸...\NDeep breath--
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.49,0:52:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 卧槽？！ - 哎 哎 哎\N- What the fuck?! - Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.02,0:52:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快救命 克拉克 - 抓紧我\N- Help us! Clark! - Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.89,0:52:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来了 来了 来了 - 救人啊 你个混蛋\N- Okay, okay, okay! - Help, you fucking asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.56,0:52:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让我解 - 快给我解开 老哥\N- Let me get it! - Untie me, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.63,0:52:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 你特么在磨蹭什么？\NWhat the hell are you doing, Clark?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.13,0:52:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我解不开 - 快点 克拉克\N- I can't! - Hurry, Clark!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.33,0:52:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我在弄了 我在弄了 - 操！\N- I'm trying, I'm trying! - FUCK!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.67,0:52:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,别松手 别松手\NDon't let go! Don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.60,0:52:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 坚持住 - 操 千万别放手\N- Hold on! - Fuck! Don't let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.50,0:52:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 千万别放手 - 我去拿...\N- Don't let me go! - Let me get at--
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.57,0:52:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博！\NBOBBY!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.14,0:52:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不 小凯 不\NNO! KAT, NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.54,0:52:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博\NBobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.64,0:52:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博！\NBOBBY!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.31,0:52:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博\NBobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.48,0:53:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事 我们得...克拉克\NWhat are we doing? We need to... Clark!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.42,0:53:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博 别 别 别\NBobby! No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.26,0:53:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,别 小凯 小凯\NOw... KAT! Kat...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.26,0:53:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博\NBobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.10,0:53:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博 不\NBobby! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.53,0:53:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,阿博 不\NBobby! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.20,0:53:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,小凯\NKat!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.54,0:53:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 该死\NOh, fuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.04,0:53:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不 不 不 不 不 不\NOh, no, no, no, no, no! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.69,0:54:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,小凯？\NKat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.76,0:54:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,小凯？\NKat?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.45,0:55:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗？\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.62,0:55:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,别过来 滚开\NStay back! Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.55,0:56:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 克拉克 我在在这...\NClark? CLARK! I'm here...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.06,0:57:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这 那东西要回来了\NI'm here! It's gonna come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.72,0:57:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,快让我进去 克拉克 求你让我进去\NPlease, Clark, please let me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.53,0:57:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 小凯？ - 让我进去\N- Kat? - Let me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.40,0:57:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你...你在在哪？\NWh-wh-where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.13,0:57:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得赶紧走 克拉克 没时间了\NWe have to go now, Clark! We have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.00,0:57:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那东西要回来了 它会找到我的\NIt's gonna come back, it's gonna find me!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.04,0:57:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,小凯 小凯？额...等等 我没搞明白 你到底在哪？\NKat! Kat? Uh... Wait, I don't understand. Wh-where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.17,0:57:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的 快让我进去\NPlease, let me the fuck in!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.98,0:57:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但这...这是堵墙啊\NBut it's a... it's-it's a wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.34,0:57:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能看到我？\NHow can-how can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.55,0:57:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我在玻璃的另一边\NI'm on the other side of the glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.21,0:57:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你怎么看得见...？ - 你怎么看不见我？\N- How can you see...? - How can you not see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.28,0:57:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,什么玻璃？你在说什么鬼话？\NWhat glass?! What the fuck are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.89,0:57:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你在...在说什...？\NWh-what are you talk--
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.02,0:57:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你那边能看到什么吗？\NOkay, can you see anything on your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.39,0:57:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,有门把手吗 还是有门？有没有入口之类的东西？\NCan you see a handle, a door? Is there a hatch, anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.13,0:57:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 没有 没有...\NNo, no, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.00,0:57:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...好吧 让我想想办法 好吗？等一下\NUh... Okay. Let me figure this out, okay? Just hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.00,0:57:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住 行吗？只是...\NHold on, okay? It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.07,0:57:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克拉克？ - 别急 别急 让我试...\N- Clark? - No, no, just let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.01,0:57:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克拉克 - 别急\N- Clark! - Just hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.64,0:57:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我找找看 - 克拉克\N- Let me figure this out! - CLARK!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.11,0:57:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别催我 我在想办法 - 克拉克 快跑\N- Let me figure this out... - Clark! Clark!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.21,0:57:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 它就在你身后\NClark, behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.59,0:58:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[诺拉·克莱...\N氯丙...]
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.27,0:58:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[【氯丙嗪：抗精神病药物】]
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.69,0:59:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽 住手\NMary!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.14,0:59:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽\NMary...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.40,0:59:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗？\Nwhat were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.17,0:59:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过绝对 绝对\NI never, ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.11,0:59:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不能出门\Never said you could go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.08,0:59:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不行\NIt's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.72,0:59:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,外面到处都是\NThey're all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.86,1:01:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,您拨打的是玛丽·克莱因医生的电话\NHi, you've reached Dr. Mary Klein.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.96,1:01:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我目前不便接听\NI'm not able to answer the call,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.06,1:01:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,请留言\Nso please leave a message,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.00,1:01:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽快给您回电\Nand I'll get back to you as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.44,1:01:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽...\NMary...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.58,1:01:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我打开那扇窗了\NI opened the window.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.85,1:01:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再回来了\NI won't be coming back.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.84,1:02:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[克船长的家具百宝库]
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.09,1:02:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,“...求你了”\N"...Please!"
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.53,1:02:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,“救救我们”\N"Save us!"
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.70,1:02:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[（1983年 异相研究所获得120万美元联邦资助开发下一代核磁共振设备）]
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.37,1:02:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,“好 我照作”\N"All right! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.60,1:02:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,“我会救你们 我会照作”\NI'll save you! I will do it!"
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.28,1:02:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,“梦翠儿！”\N"Moon Child!"
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.13,1:02:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[电影《大魔域》1984：讲述一个男孩通过想象力重建世界的奇幻故事]
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.42,1:02:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道你手之前碰过什么\NI don't know where that hand's been.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.67,1:02:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[【《大魔域》英文片名：直译为“永不结束的故事”】]
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.06,1:02:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,“哟 伙计们 瞧瞧这儿啊！”\N"Well, ahoy there, mateys!"
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.03,1:02:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,“按照这藏宝图”\N"Now, according to me map,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.46,1:02:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,“咱们现在已经登上了这片宝地”\N"we've landed on the crystal shores of a bountiful land,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.10,1:02:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,“这里的折扣简直是在倒贴啊！”\N"a land filled with great deals."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.63,1:02:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[（全市最低价）]
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.00,1:02:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,“你也赶紧赶紧抛锚靠岸！”\N"So drop your anchors and come on down
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.24,1:02:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,“快来克船长的家具百宝库！”\N"to Cap'n Clark's Ottoman Empire."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.04,1:02:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,“潜入这场顶级家具海洋吧”\N"Get lost in an endless sea
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.68,1:03:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,“桌椅沙发 卧室全套 样样齐全！”\N"of quality tables, chairs, couches, and bedroom sets."
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.35,1:03:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,“想给小海盗配上下铺？”\N"Need bed bunks for the scallywagses quarters?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.95,1:03:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,“来这儿就对了！”\N"W've got it all!"
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.12,1:03:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,“价格低到...”\N"And at prices so low
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.29,1:03:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,“你都觉得在抢钱啊！”\N"you'll think that yo're robbing me!"
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.55,1:03:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗？\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.80,1:03:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[大促销 大降价]
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.40,1:03:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗？\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.27,1:04:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[大促销 大降价]
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.37,1:04:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克？\NClark?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.06,1:04:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[无需信用卡]
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.89,1:04:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克 你在哪儿？\NClark, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.64,1:04:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[楼下更精彩]
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.93,1:04:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克？\NClark?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.94,1:05:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[车停]
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.19,1:05:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[家具店 和 入口]
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.04,1:07:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克？\NClark?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.29,1:09:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[（平面图又变了 屋顶不对 屋顶绝对不对 这图纸是谁签的名？但这笔迹 像我的）]
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.77,1:09:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[（管他的什么超自然 理智点吧）]
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.80,1:09:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[（此刻和此地是相通的）]
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.07,1:10:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,克拉克？\NClark?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.67,1:10:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你总算发现了\NYou found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.55,1:10:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么躲起来？\NWhy are you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.52,1:10:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你太吵了\NYou were being too loud.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.07,1:11:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在哪？\NWhere are we?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.74,1:11:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这里...\NIt's...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.51,1:11:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是所有存在过的地方\N...every place that ever was.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.45,1:11:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这儿多久了？\NHow long have you been here?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.49,1:11:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么声音？\NWhat was that?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.67,1:11:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,别紧张\NStay calm.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.81,1:11:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没别人\NIt's only me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.78,1:11:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你是了解我的\NYou know me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.71,1:12:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.51,1:12:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,都是为了你好\NThis is for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.84,1:14:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在现实生活中\NAs you walk through life,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.37,1:14:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,缺乏引导的心灵 总会走入死循环 养成固有的习惯\Nthe untrained mind accumulates loops, habits...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.08,1:14:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,总是重蹈覆辙\N...behaviors that keep you drifting in circles,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.69,1:14:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,陷入相同的问题\Ncreating the same problems,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.06,1:14:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,总是用同样的办法\Nreaching for the same solutions
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.69,1:14:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一遍又一遍\Nover and over again.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.40,1:15:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟神经通路就爱走阻力最小的路径\NStill, it's the neural pathway of least resistance.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.91,1:15:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这条路径是我自己铺的\NThe one I made.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.74,1:15:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候\NThe one that kept me safe...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.71,1:15:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这套防线保护了我\Nwhen I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.05,1:15:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你看...\NYou know...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.92,1:15:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我学会了抢在被伤害之前 把别人推开\NI learned to push people away before they could hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.25,1:15:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,而现在 我都成年了\NAnd, now, as an adult,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.09,1:15:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,还是留在原地\NI'm still stuck right where I started.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.93,1:15:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一个人\NAlone.